      1231,
      1946
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Áp dụng AM-GM: } 18x + \\frac{180000}{x} \\ge 2\\sqrt{18x \\cdot \\frac{180000}{x}} = 2\\sqrt{3240000} = 3600.\n$$"
  },
